\v 1 Kwasekusithi-ke ngomnyaka wamatshumi amathathu, nge\add nyanga\add* yesine, ngolwesihlanu lwenyanga\x + 1.3. Nani 4.3.\x*, lapho ngangiphakathi kwabathunjiweyo ngasemfuleni iKebari\x + 1.3. 3.15,23. 10.15,20,22. 43.3. 2 Kho. 17.6. 18.11.\x*, avuleka amazulu\x + Mat. 3.16. Mark. 1.10. Luka 3.21. Joha. 1.51. Seb. 7.56.10.11. Isam. 19.11. Isam. 4.1.\x*, ngasengibona imibono kaNkulunkulu\x + 8.3. 40.2. 11.24. Nani 12.6.\x*.
\v 2 Ngolwesihlanu lwenyanga, okungumnyaka wesihlanu\x + 8.1. 20.1. 24.1. 29.1. 26.1. 30.20. 31.1. 33.21. 32.1,17. 40.1. 29.17.\x* wokuthunjwa kwenkosi uJehoyakhini\x + 33.21. 40.1. 2 Kho. 24.12,15.\x*,
\v 3 ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* leza liqonde kuHezekeli, indodana kaBuzi, umpristi\x + 1.3. Nani 4.3.\x*\x + Jer. 1.1.\x*, elizweni lamaKhaladiya ngasemfuleni iKebari\x + 1.3. 3.15,23. 10.15,20,22. 43.3. 2 Kho. 17.6. 18.11.\x*; lesandla seN\nd kosi\nd* saba phezu kwakhe lapho\x + 8.1. 3.22. 33.22. 37.1. 2 Kho. 3.15.\x*.
