\v 4 Ngasengibona, khangela-ke, umoya wesivunguzane\x + 3.12. Jer. 23.19. 25.32. 30.23. Jobe 38.1.\x* wavela enyakatho, iyezi elikhulu, lomlilo ozimumetheyo\x + Jer. 1.13.\x*, lokucwazimula inhlangothi zonke zalo\x + 1.27.\x*, laphakathi kwalo kwavela kwangathi libala lethusi, livela phakathi komlilo\x + 1.27.\x*\x + 8.2.\x*\x + 1.7,16,22,27. 8.2. 10.9. Levi 13.55. Nani 11.7.\x*.
\v 5 Laphakathi kwalo kwavela umfanekiso wezidalwa ezine eziphilayo\x + Isam. 4.6.\x*. Lalokhu kwakuyisimo sazo\x + 10.8.\x*: Zazilomfanekiso womuntu\x + 1.10. 10.14,21.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo yileso laleso sasilobuso obune, njalo yileso laleso sazo sasilempiko ezine\x + 1.10. 10.14,21.\x*.
\v 7 Lenyawo zazo zazizinyawo eziqondileyo, lengaphansi yezinyawo zazo yayinjengengaphansi yonyawo lwethole, zacwazimula njengombala wethusi elilolongiweyo\x + 40.3. Dan. 10.6. Isam. 1.15. 2.18.\x*\x + 1.7,16,22,27. 8.2. 10.9. Levi 13.55. Nani 11.7.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo kwakulezandla zomuntu ngaphansi kwempiko zazo\x + 10.8,21.\x* enhlangothini zazo zozine\x + 1.17. 10.11. 43.16,17.\x*. Njalo zozine zazilobuso bazo lempiko zazo\x + 10.8,21.\x*.
\v 9 Impiko zazo\x + 1.11.\x* zazihlangene olunye kolunye\x + 1.23. 3.13. Eks. 26.3. Levi 18.18.\x*; aziphendukanga ekuhambeni kwazo\x + 1.12,17. 10.11.\x*; zahamba, yileso laleso siqonde phambili\x + 1.12.10.22.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo umfanekiso wobuso bazo wawuyibuso bomuntu, njalo zozine zazilobuso besilwane ngakwesokunene; njalo zozine zazilobuso benkabi ngakwesokhohlo; futhi zozine zazilobuso belinqe\x + 10.14. Isam. 4.7.\x*.
\v 11 Babunjalo ubuso bazo; lempiko zazo zazehlukene ngaphezulu; yileso laleso sasilezimbili zihlanganisiwe kolunye\x + 1.11.\x*, lezimbili zigubuzele imizimba yazo\x + 1.23. Isa. 6.2.\x*.
\v 12 Zahamba yileso laleso siqonde phambili\x + 1.12. 10.22.\x*; zaya lapho umoya owaya khona\x + 1.20.\x*, zingaphenduki ekuhambeni kwazo\x + 1.12,17. 10.11.\x*.
\v 13 Mayelana lomfanekiso wezidalwa eziphilayo, ukubonakala kwazo kwakunjengamalahle omlilo avuthayo\x + 10.2. Hlab. 18.12,13. 140.10. Hlab. 120.4.\x*, njengokubonakala kwezibane; kwahamba kusiya le lale phakathi kwezidalwa eziphilayo; njalo umlilo wawulokukhazimula, njalo emlilweni kwakuphuma umbane\x + Isam. 4.5. Eks. 20.18.\x*.
\v 14 Lezidalwa eziphilayo zagijima\x + 1.18. Zek. 4.10.\x* zaphenduka njengokubonakala kokuphazima kombane\x + Dan. 10.6. Mat. 24.27. Luka 17.24.\x*.
