\v 15 Ngathi ngikhangela izidalwa eziphilayo, khangela-ke, ivili elilodwa lalisemhlabeni eceleni kwezidalwa eziphilayo, ebusweni baso obune\x + 10.9. 10.2,6. Dan. 7.9.\x*.
\v 16 Ukubonakala kwamavili lomsebenzi wawo\x + 10.9. 10.2,6. Dan. 7.9.\x* kwakufanana lombala\x + 10.9. 10.2,6. Dan. 7.9.\x* \w webherule\w**\x + 28.13. Dan. 10.6. Isam. 21.20.\x*; njalo zozine zazilesimo sinye\x + 10.10.\x*; lokubonakala kwazo lomsebenzi wazo kwakunjengokuthi livili phakathi kwevili\x + 10.10.\x*.
\v 17 Ekuhambeni kwawo\x + 10.11.\x* ahamba ngezinhlangothi zawo zozine\x + 1.8.\x*; kawaphendukanga ekuhambeni kwawo\x + 1.9.\x*.
\v 18 Mayelana lamarimu awo, ayephakeme kangangokuthi ayesesabeka; njalo amarimu awo ayegcwele\x + 10.12.\x* amehlo inhlangothi zonke zawo zozine\x + 1.18. Zek. 4.10.\x*.
\v 19 Ekuhambeni kwezidalwa eziphilayo amavili ahamba eceleni kwazo\x + 1.21. 10.16.\x*; lekuphakanyisweni kwezidalwa eziphilayo emhlabeni lamavili aphakanyiswa\x + 1.20,21.\x*.
\v 20 Lapho umoya owawusiya khona zaya khona, kulapho umoya owawuzakuya khona\x + 1.12. 10.17.\x*; lamavili aphakanyiswa eqondene lawo\x + 1.20,21.\x*; ngoba umoya wezidalwa eziphilayo wawusemavilini\x + 1.20,21.\x*.
\v 21 Lapho lezi zihamba, \add lawo\add* ahamba\x + 1.19,20.\x*; lalapho lezi zisima, \add lawo\add* ema\x + 10.17.\x*; lalapho lezi ziphakanyiswa emhlabeni\x + 1.20,21.\x*, amavili aphakanyiswa eqondene lazo\x + 10.19.\x*; ngoba umoya wezidalwa eziphilayo wawusemavilini\x + 1.20,21.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo isimo somkhathi ngaphezu kwamakhanda ezidalwa eziphilayo\x + 1.25,26. 10.1. 10.20.\x* sasinjengombala \w wekristali\w** elesabekayo\x + Isam. 4.6.\x*, seluliwe phezu kwamakhanda azo ngaphezulu.
\v 23 Langaphansi komkhathi impiko zazo zaziqondile\x + 1.7.\x*, olunye lusiya kolunye; yileso laleso silezimbili ezembese imizimba yazo ngapha, njalo yileso laleso silezimbili ezembese ngaphayana\x + 1.11.\x*.
\v 24 Lekuhambeni kwazo ngezwa umsindo wempiko zazo\x + 10.5.\x* \add u\add*njengomsindo wamanzi amanengi\x + 43.2. Hlab. 29.3. Isam. 1.15.\x*, njengelizwi\x + 10.5.\x*\x + Jobe 37.4,5. Hlab. 29.3,4. 68.33.\x* likaSomandla\x + Gen. 17.1. Ruthe 1.20,21. Jobe 5.17. Hlab. 68.14. 91.1. Isa. 13.6. Jow. 1.15.\x*, umsindo wokuhlokoma\x + Jer. 11.16.\x*, njengomsindo wenkamba; lapho zisima zehlisa impiko zazo\x + Dan. 10.6. Isam. 19.6.\x*.
\v 25 Kwasekusiba lelizwi elavela phezu komkhathi ongaphezu kwekhanda lazo lapho sezimi sezehlise impiko zazo\x + 10.19.\x*.
